Setup crosser user (nologin) 
install missing INSTALLED-APPS
install nginx & copy nginx config into sites-available
symlink config into sites-enabled
create postgres user
create postgres database 
edit /crosser_web/settings.py for database + password
initialize database vi ./manage.py  (remember the default data fixtures!)
test
turn off DEBUG=true in settings.py
generate static files (./manage.py collectstatic)


rabbitmq:
  sudo aptitude install rabbitmq-server
  sudo rabbitmqctl
  sudo rabbitmqctl add_user rabbit c14h2002
  sudo rabbitmqctl add_vhost /django_crosser



